OL,6,FA family say they are mystified about
OL,7,Fwhy their home was covered in blue
OL,8,Fpaint in a vandal attack by two quad
OL,9,Fbikers.
OL,11,FThe period property, in North Anston,
OL,12,Fnear Rotherham, , was left damaged
OL,13,Ffollowing the incident on Saturday, 27
OL,14,FApril.
OL,16,FIn video captured on the family's CCTV
OL,17,Fcamera, two men can be seen
OL,18,Fapproaching the house on Ryton Road
OL,19,Fand using a canister to shower the
OL,20,Fdoor, windows and walls with paint
OL,21,Fbefore driving off.
