OL,6,FOwner Jayne, who asked not to be named
OL,7,Fin full, said she had spent the last
OL,8,Fdecade carefully restoring the house
OL,9,Fand has no idea why it was targeted.
OL,11,F"The only thing we can think of is
OL,12,Fthat it was the wrong house," she said.
OL,14,F"Let's hope it was the wrong house
OL,15,Fbecause I am worried that if it was
OL,16,Fmeant to be us then something will
OL,17,Fhappen again."
OL,19,FEfforts to clean the property since
OL,20,Fthe attack have been futile.
