OL,6,FJayne's daughter Bec said: "Obviously
OL,7,Fit won't come off, it leaves just like
OL,8,Fa residue. It has been jet washed and
OL,9,Fnothing moves. It has been wiped and
OL,10,Fit doesn't come off.
OL,12,F"My mum keeps the blind closed now as
OL,13,Fshe doesn't want to see it."
OL,15,FJayne and her family are hoping that
OL,16,Fthe paint will eventually be able to
OL,17,Fbe removed from the detached house.
